ATHLETICS - KENYA ' S AGUTA STILL UNCONSCIOUS . Boston marathon champion Lameck Aguta was still unconscious on Wednesday , four days after he was admitted to hospital following a car accident , his twin brother Zachary Nyambaso said on Wednesday . Doctors said his condition was still stable and they would issue a bulletin if there were any changes . Kenyan Aguta , also the Commonwealth 10 , 000 metres champion , sustained head injuries in the crash but a brain scan showed no serious damage . Doctors , who had said on Monday they were encouraged by his condition , were concerned on Wednesday that the athlete was still unconscious and that his condition remained largely unchanged . Police said Aguta was injured when his car went out of control and landed in a ditch in his native Rift Valley province . The driver of the car and another man were slightly injured . 
